    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the East coast, crazy street</h2><br>Playing as Joe, an undercover agent working for Jimmy Craster, you have to become test subject number 47 to learn how the Acronym works and gain access to the Space-changing Ball.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...From the background</h2>&quot;You heard that, Joe,&quot; Jimmy said over the comm<br>- You have to find and disable this fucking ball!<br>- Wipe everyone off the face of the earth, but give me back the Acronym!<br>- Can you hear me?<br>&quot;Don't let an old friend down, Joe<br><br>Immerse yourself in the world of parallel dreams, together with Amanda-Service, to fulfill all your desires!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lady of Dreams</h2>This is an action-rhythm bagel, whose actions take place in a dream, where music and thoughts merged in one harmony!<br>The environment and missions are created based on your chosen favorite composition. With each completed stage, the game will change its rules…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > In some cases you have to fight in the subway under ELECTRONIC ROCK</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/c636afbaa868bce484dcd60e13cb7352.poster.avif?t=1726310832\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/c636afbaa868bce484dcd60e13cb7352.webm?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/c636afbaa868bce484dcd60e13cb7352.mp4?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In others, cut a bunch of people under Dubstep</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/232b19cb7e3687b6e75c9893f5a360ca.poster.avif?t=1726310832\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/232b19cb7e3687b6e75c9893f5a360ca.webm?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/232b19cb7e3687b6e75c9893f5a360ca.mp4?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Third, have fun on the planet Marcean, and destroy everything...</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/5a629786743d72b4df9290c2461e2070.poster.avif?t=1726310832\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/5a629786743d72b4df9290c2461e2070.webm?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/5a629786743d72b4df9290c2461e2070.mp4?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > But that's not all... You may find yourself in the epicenter of hell listening to METAL ROCK</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/2c89b9906cc74cbea65d14bf797c8cfe.poster.avif?t=1726310832\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/2c89b9906cc74cbea65d14bf797c8cfe.webm?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116280/extras/2c89b9906cc74cbea65d14bf797c8cfe.mp4?t=1726310832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I'll be happy to guide Joe through your parallel worlds. (c) Karen.</h2>",
